{
  "stem": "9995.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Except not during high holidays because we were living far away from it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if you could not travel by car or whatever, we were going to so-called old synagogue, which was built in the 14th century.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was right next to the house where my grandfather has.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Right now, this is a museum.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we, of course, observe Passover and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] many-- all the holidays, actually.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Until I went to gymnasium, when there was a very big thing because school was also held on Saturday.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And grandfather was the boss, not my father or anybody.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just grandfather as what we call in Latin paterfamilias.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, at any rate, he gave permission for me, providing I wouldn't write on Saturday.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I had permission not to write, but I was going to school on Saturday.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Before-- during elementary school, six grades, I was not attending school on Saturdays.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The first six years that was like here, elementary school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then elementary school had also seventh grade.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If you did not take examination for gymnasium, or you didn't pass it, then you are going to seventh grade and then to some trade school or whatever for eight, nine grade.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But here, this was four years of gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And after this, you pass-- they call it [NON-ENGLISH], in German, [GERMAN] In Italian, [ITALIAN] They have the same system all over Europe.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then was [NON-ENGLISH] for two years, which was more specialized.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Either you took classic things, which also besides Latin was Greek, or you took mathematical, physical.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And with my problem was I did not reach that far.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was young.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we were already considering because I was good in both.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was very good also in math and in sciences.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
